>
> > system.time(sav <- cooks.distance(res2, cluster=dat$group,
> reestimate=FALSE))
>    user  system elapsed
> 270.960   0.044 271.005
>
> ### with OpenBLAS
>
> > system.time(res1 <- rma.mv(yi, vi, random = ~ 1 |
> group/district/school, data=dat))
>    user  system elapsed
>  86.531   8.707  95.242
> >
> > system.time(res2 <- rma.mv(yi, vi, random = ~ 1 |
